    <div class="price-card">
      <div class="price-amount">$199</div>
      <div class="price-label">Full chimney inspection &amp; clean</div>
      <ul class="price-includes">
        <li>Full sweep from firebox to pot</li>
        <li>Flue clean &amp; soot removal</li>
        <li>Creosote &amp; blockage check</li>
        <li>Bird nest removal if present</li>
        <li>Verbal condition report</li>
        <li>No call-out fee</li>
      </ul>
      <a class="btn-primary" href="tel:0476302729">Book Now — 0476 302 729</a>
    </div>
  </section>

  <!-- LOCAL KNOWLEDGE -->
  <section class="local-section" id="local">
    <h2>Chimney Sweeping in South Yarra</h2>
    <div class="local-box"><p>South Yarra is one of Melbourne's most established and sought-after inner suburbs, developed from the 1860s on the high ground south of the Yarra River overlooking the CBD. The residential streets north of Toorak Road are characterised by Victorian terrace houses, double-fronted Edwardian cottages and substantial interwar apartments, a large proportion of which retain their original chimney and fireplace systems. The southern end of South Yarra, toward the Toorak border, transitions to larger single-storey and double-storey period homes with generous land and multiple original fireplaces. South Yarra's elevated position and proximity to the Yarra River valley creates a winter cold pattern where cold air drains from the higher ground to the south and east and pools along the lower streets close to the river, with the river corridor adding a damp, still cold to winter mornings that makes a well-functioning fireplace genuinely valuable. The suburb's renovation market is strong — owners invest significantly in maintaining original features including working fireplaces, and professional chimney maintenance is a normal part of annual property upkeep for many South Yarra homes. We service South Yarra regularly and are familiar with the terrace and period home chimney configurations throughout the suburb.</p></div>
  </section>

  <!-- SIGNS -->
  <section class="signs-section" id="signs">
    <h2>Signs Your South Yarra Chimney Needs Cleaning</h2>
    <ul class="signs-list">
      <li>Smoke pushing back into the room when the fire is lit</li>
      <li>A smoky or stale smell around the fireplace when the system is not in use</li>
      <li>Soot marking on the original plasterwork or mantle surround</li>
      <li>A flue that is overdue for cleaning after multiple winters of use</li>
      <li>A previously sealed fireplace being reopened after a renovation</li>
    </ul>
  </section>

  <!-- SERVICES -->
  <section class="services-section" id="services">
    <h2>Chimney Services in South Yarra</h2>
    <div class="services-grid">
      <div class="service-card"><h3>Chimney Sweep</h3><p>Full brush sweep from firebox to pot. Soot, creosote and debris removed. Verbal condition report included.</p></div>
      <div class="service-card"><h3>Flue Cleaning</h3><p>Thorough flue clean using professional brushes and equipment. Removes accumulated creosote and restores full draw.</p></div>
      <div class="service-card"><h3>Wood Heater Service</h3><p>Slow combustion heater flue clean and inspection. Baffle check, door seal inspection, full flue swept top to bottom.</p></div>
      <div class="service-card"><h3>Chimney Inspection</h3><p>Visual inspection of firebox, flue, damper, crown and pot. Written report available on request. Included in the $199 service.</p></div>
    </div>
  </section>

  <!-- REVIEWS -->
  <section class="reviews-section" id="reviews">
    <h2>What South Yarra Customers Say</h2>
    <div class="reviews-grid">
      <div class="review-card"><div class="review-stars">&#9733;&#9733;&#9733;&#9733;&#9733;</div><p class="review-text">&ldquo;Victorian terrace on the South Yarra ridge. David cleaned the flue, checked the pot and gave a clear report on the chimney condition. Fireplace draws perfectly — will be booking every year.&rdquo;</p><p class="review-author">Isabella T., South Yarra</p></div>
      <div class="review-card"><div class="review-stars">&#9733;&#9733;&#9733;&#9733;&#9733;</div><p class="review-text">&ldquo;We had the front and rear fireplaces both cleaned. David worked carefully around the original tiling and marble surrounds. Thorough and professional — exactly what you want.&rdquo;</p><p class="review-author">Oliver N., South Yarra</p></div>
      <div class="review-card"><div class="review-stars">&#9733;&#9733;&#9733;&#9733;&#9733;</div><p class="review-text">&ldquo;Reopened a fireplace after our renovation and called Dave to inspect and clean the flue before we used it. He found a large bird nest and significant debris — really glad we didn't just light it. Excellent service.&rdquo;</p><p class="review-author">Emma G., South Yarra</p></div>
    </div>
  </section>

  <!-- ABOUT -->
  <section class="about-section" id="about">
    <h2>About Dave&rsquo;s Chimney Sweeping</h2>
    <p>Dave&rsquo;s Chimney Sweeping is a local, owner-operated business covering Melbourne's inner eastern suburbs including South Yarra. Dave personally handles every job &mdash; no subcontractors, no call centres. Flat $199 rate per chimney, no hidden fees.</p>
    <a class="btn-secondary" href="tel:0476302729">Call Dave — 0476 302 729</a>
  </section>

  <!-- FAQs -->
  <section class="faq-section" id="faq">
    <h2>Chimney Sweep South Yarra — FAQs</h2>
    {faqs.map(f => (
    <details>
      <summary>{f.q}</summary>
      <p>{f.a}</p>
    </details>
    ))}
  </section>

  <!-- BOOKING FORM -->
  <section class="booking-section" id="booking">
    <h2>Book a Chimney Sweep in South Yarra</h2>
    <form action="https://formspree.io/f/xdkobvpv" method="POST" class="booking-form">
      <input type="hidden" name="suburb" value="South Yarra 3141" />
      <label>Name <input type="text" name="name" required /></label>
      <label>Phone <input type="tel" name="phone" required /></label>
      <label>Email <input type="email" name="email" /></label>
      <label>Message <textarea name="message" rows="3">Chimney sweep enquiry — South Yarra 3141</textarea></label>
      <button type="submit" class="btn-primary">Send Enquiry</button>
    </form>
  </section>

  <!-- NEARBY SUBURBS -->
  <section class="nearby-section" id="nearby">
    <h2>Nearby Areas We Service</h2>
    <div class="suburb-chips">
      <a class="suburb-chip" href="/chimney-sweeping/richmond">Richmond 3121</a>
      <a class="suburb-chip" href="/chimney-sweeping/hawthorn">Hawthorn 3122</a>
      <a class="suburb-chip" href="/chimney-sweeping/malvern">Malvern 3144</a>
      <a class="suburb-chip" href="/chimney-sweeping/prahran">Prahran 3181</a>
      <a class="suburb-chip" href="/chimney-sweeping/malvern">Toorak 3142</a>
    </div>
  </section>

  <!-- BREADCRUMB -->
  <nav class="breadcrumb" aria-label="Breadcrumb">
    <a href="/">Home</a> &rsaquo; <a href="/#service-areas">Service Areas</a> &rsaquo; South Yarra
  </nav>

  <!-- BOTTOM CTA -->
  <section class="bottom-cta">
    <h2>Ready to book your South Yarra chimney sweep?</h2>
    <p>$199 flat rate &mdash; no call-out fee &mdash; same-week bookings available.</p>
    <a class="btn-primary" href="tel:0476302729">Call 0476 302 729</a>
  </section>

  <!-- STICKY MOBILE CTA -->
  <a href="tel:0476302729" id="sticky-cta" aria-label="Call or text Dave">
    <span id="sticky-icon">&#128222;</span>
    <span id="sticky-text">Call/Text Dave</span>
  </a>
  <style>
    #sticky-cta{position:fixed;bottom:1.25rem;right:1.25rem;z-index:999;display:flex;align-items:center;gap:.5rem;background:#e07b00;color:#fff;font-weight:700;font-size:1rem;padding:.75rem 1.25rem;border-radius:999px;box-shadow:0 4px 16px rgba(0,0,0,.25);text-decoration:none;transition:opacity .3s;opacity:0;pointer-events:none;}
    #sticky-cta.visible{opacity:1;pointer-events:auto}
    @media(min-width:768px){#sticky-cta{display:none}}
  </style>
  <script is:inline>
    (function(){
      var btn = document.getElementById('sticky-cta');
      var hero = document.querySelector('.hero');
      function check(){
        var threshold = hero ? hero.offsetHeight : 300;
        if(window.scrollY > threshold){ btn.classList.add('visible'); }
        else { btn.classList.remove('visible'); }
      }
      window.addEventListener('scroll', check, {passive:true});
      check();
    })();
  </script>

</MainLayout>
